Adds a server into records. Services will recognise it as a authorised server for the network,
and will be listed in the SPLITEDSERVERS command if the server splits away. The <NUMERIC> of 
the server must be the same as the one in the M-line of that server.

EXAMPLE: /msg %OS% ADDSERVER IRC.Severious.Com.Sg 6 GeNeXiS
SEEALSO: DELSERVER LISTSERVERS SPLITEDSERVERS